\section{Interactive app}{

\code{\link{ltm_app}()} constructs the packaged Shiny application, and
\code{\link{run_ltm_app}()} launches it. The app exposes the core workflow
for selecting locations, retrieving Sentinel-2 data, preprocessing time
series, running breakpoint detection, and downloading tabular results.
}

